CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 23, 1950, pg. 22, reads: "Triumphant Partners - Tom Alexander and Juanita Page are shown being awarded a trophy for their thrilling win in mix doubles at the recent pre-holiday bowling tournament. Eugene Clark is making the presentation. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Eugene Clark on right, presenting bowling trophies to Tom Alexander and Juanita Page, for mix doubles bowling tournament, in lane of bowling alley
